<p>Get the recommended rectangle to draw a caret.</p>


<pre class="language-csharp"><code class="language-csharp">public SkiaSharp.SKRect CaretRectangle { get; }</code></pre>

<h2 id="remarks">Remarks</h2><p>This will be based on the <em>previous</em> character on this line (or the same character
if this is first character in the line). The caret should be drawn as a line from
the rectangle's top-right to bottom-left.  Usually the rectangle will be zero width
(ie: a vertical line), except when over italic text in which case it will be slanted.</p>

